cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.DS 

This paper is about image classification using neural networks, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also introduces a method to sparsify DenseNet, which is a technique related to neural network architecture (cs.LG). The use of an attention module is also mentioned, which is a technique related to neural network optimization (cs.NE) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper discusses the efficiency of the proposed SparseNet, which is related to data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
